🔐 Password Strength Checker & Generator (GUI Version)
Desktop Security Utility Built with Python & Tkinter
Developed by Rishikesh Borah
📌 Project Overview

Password security is one of the most important foundations of cybersecurity.

Many users still create weak passwords such as:

123456
password
admin123
qwerty

These passwords are vulnerable to:

Brute Force Attacks
Dictionary Attacks
Credential Stuffing
Account Takeover
Password Guessing

This project solves that problem by creating an interactive desktop application that allows users to:

✔ Check password strength
✔ Generate secure passwords
✔ Get improvement suggestions
✔ Copy generated passwords instantly
✔ View password score visually

Built completely in Python using Tkinter GUI Framework.

Project implementation is based on your uploaded GUI application.

